OK then, that is it for today's episode on Robert Baden-Powell and The Boy Scouts.

00:19:56.271 --> 00:20:01.461
I hope it's been an interesting one, that you've learnt something new, and even if you were a

00:20:01.461 --> 00:20:06.631
Scout when you were younger, then you learned something new about this amazing global movement.

